<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/30746586-duane"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1399284033i/30746586._UY100_CR18,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
