        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer327214669" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4302622902434448175">This book disturbed my peace with the universe. I read it while I was working on a death penalty case some years back, mostly on the bus too and from work. It led to me spending no little time starring out the window. Trembling ontologically.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


