<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/161812.Evil_in_Modern_Thought"><img alt="Evil in Modern Thought: An Alternative History of Philosophy" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1348765236l/161812._SX98_.jpg" />
